text: The Star of Nanchang (Chinese:南昌之星 or Chinese:南昌之星摩天轮) is a 525 ft (160-metre) tall giant Ferris wheel. It is in the eastern Chinese city of Nanchang, which is the capital of Jiangxi Province. Category:Buildings and structures in China Category:Ferris wheels Category:Jiangxi
title: Star of Nanchang
